text: Seize this rare chance to secure the final lot at gorgeous Creekside Meadows! This 1acre plot. 22979 Methow Court is more than land it's a chance to embrace a lifestyle highlighted by sweeping mountain and territorial views near Mount Vernon, blending rural charm with city convenience. This impressive community offers shared access to 68 acres of open space, perfect for nature enthusiasts. It comes utility-ready with PUD water, power, natural gas, septic design, and permitensuring a seamless build. Just 4 miles to I- 5, enjoy easy access to amenities while maintaining a serene lifestyle. Homes must be over 1800 sf, ensuring elegance. This is a rare opportunity to build in a premium picturesque setting of convenient country living.

Farmington Square, a prestigious 55+ gated community in Burlington. Great location across from clubhouse, community garden & extra parking. Charming home with 3 bdrms, 1.75 baths, living rm w/vaulted ceiling & gas fireplace open to dining. Kitchen w/loads of cabinets, newer appliances, gas range & upgraded tile backsplash. Beautiful craftsmanship with high ceilings & trim provides a spacious feel & comfort throughout. Primary bdrm with walk-in shower & large walk-in closet. Spacious laundry room & pantry space. Deep single car garage attached w/storage cabinets & attic storage above. Exterior maintenance & landscaping included. Convenient location to town & I-5.

Welcome to your charming and well-appointed home in the perfect location! This remodeled mid-century gem in Old Town boasts classic details at every turn and has been freshly painted for a modern touch. The stylish kitchen will make doing dishes a pleasure, while the main level features 2 bedrooms, a full bath, hardwood floors, and a cozy gas fireplace. Downstairs, discover a spacious rec room, convenient 3/4 bath, a walk-in closet, and large storage/utility/laundry room with backyard access. Outside, the mature landscaping creates a serene oasis, perfect for entertaining in the amazing outdoor living spaces. And don't forget the detached 2-car garage with bonus shop a rare find! Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this home yours.
nearby_schools: Anacortes School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Indulge in the tranquility of waterfront living at this charming retreat on the shores of Dewey Beach. With breathtaking views of Whidbey, Hope & Skagit Islands complemented by majestic Cascade Range rising beyond the horizon. 2-bedroom, 1.5-bathroom home boasting oak floors, a bright sunroom, and expansive panoramic windows framing the stunning vistas. Spacious deck with built-in seating invites you to savor outdoor gatherings while soaking in the beauty of the surroundings. Explore the tidelands with your kayaks.100Ft of your own beach waterfront. A detached 2-car garage and workshop provide ample space for hobbies and storage. Whether you seek peaceful solitude or adventures, this coastal sanctuary promises an idyllic escape.

Beautiful waterfront lot is now available for sale! Water, electric and high speed internet available. Glenhaven Lakes Club offers private heated pool, fully stocked fishing lake, boat ramp, clubhouse, tennis court and multiple private parks. Situated 20 minutes from either Bellingham or Burlington. Buyer to verify all the information.

Move in Ready! Bring your updates to this magnificent home located in a desirable neighborhood. This 4 bedroom, 3 bath, 2299sf home sits in the Hilltop Haven community. Home features hardwood floors, Crown Moulding, a Sunroom with a Northwestern view across the Skagit Valley. Included is a deck off back with a private backyard with fruit trees, a greenhouse and room for a garden. Gutters have installed a leaf and debris resistant system. Newer roof in great condition, sprinkler system, and a built-in home vacuum system located in the huge crawlspace. Don't forget to check out the 3-car garage, where one side was used as an office space. So much to offer and sits right on a Cul-de-sac and close to many community services.

Look no further! You will love the many comforts of this fully updated rambler w/large SHOP & ADU. Welcoming covered front porch, open concept w/2 living areas, 4 bdrms, 2.5 baths in 2528 sq ft. The 1152 sq ft 3-bay garage/shop has room for all your toys! Efficient heat pump w/mini splits for heating/AC & wood burning stove. Gorgeous baths & kitchen; stainless, granite, tons of cabinets, island, bfast bar & dining rm. Primary suite has great closet space, hrdwd flrs, custom walkin surround shower & French doors to the large deck & fenced backyard. Guest bathroom includes laundry area & lots of storage. Modern flooring & lighting throughout. On the outskirts of town yet minutes to I-5 & all amenities. 5 minute stroll to Little Mountain Park!

EXTRA LARGE lot with a HUGE 2640 sqft rambler, could potentially purchase adjacent city lot. TWO kitchens, 3 beds, 4 baths, and a spacious shop/card room (30ft x 32ft) with a commercial Honeywell smokeeter Built in 2005, featuring enduring quality. Carport for boat, garage with card room for RV/boat. Kitchen with ample cabinetry, 4 stoves, stainless steel fridge. Has 3 exterior electric awnings. Has an outside studio card room. Near Little Cranberry & hiking trails. Landscaped with fig, apple, and Asian pear trees. Tranquil retreat with access to amenities. Schedule your viewing today!

Welcome to this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem nestled in a prime location close to downtown and the interstate. This well-maintained home offers comfort, convenience, and a turnkey lifestyle. Open-concept design creates a warm and inviting atmosphere. The living room is perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. The primary bedroom features an three piece bathroom with nice finishes. This home has been meticulously cared for, ensuring a move-in-ready experience.

The perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this two-story, four bedroom, 2.5 baths. Ideal for anyone wanting ample space. With the addition of a closet the den/office could become a fifth bedroom. The kitchen is designed for convenience, with lots of storage, a pantry, SS appliances and ample counterspace. A light bright dining room and separate laundry room enhance the comfort of this home. Double garage, and driveway provides plenty of parking for you and your guests. Outdoors is a fully fenced patio area with a gate to the community park. Community park offers walking trails, playground, basketball court, and RV parking!

Nestled in the desirable Cedar Heights community is this impeccably maintained 3 bed/2.5 bath home! Welcomed by a covered front porch, the main floor features fresh paint throughout. Living room leads to open concept dining, family room & kitchen with stainless steel appliances, new quartz countertops, and freshened cabinetry. Bay windows overlook the private fully-fenced backyard including poured patio for entertaining, backed to a quiet greenbelt! Laundry room located off the guest bath and 2-car garage access nearby. Upstairs you are greeted with a bright & spacious vaulted-ceiling primary bedroom with vinyl plank flooring and en suite bath. Down the hall boasts 2 more bedrooms and updated full bath. Welcome Home!

This 3 bedroom, 1 3/4 bath home is an absolute jewel! There's not one thing that needs to be done before moving in - everything has been updated, painted, replaced and even the yard is newly landscaped. All appliances are high end and are included in sale.. A heat pump has been added for air conditioning. Back yard is fully fenced and has some lovely trees. Convenient location on Mount Vernon hill and just minutes away from all services. Perfect for first-time homebuyers or anyone looking to downsize or have single level living.

Investment Opportunity-One Level Triplex. Well maintained & managed three unit '50's-built income property near park and Burlington-Edison High School. One duplex building has 2, 1 bedroom, 1 bath units, each 758SF w/carport & storage locker. Third unit is a free standing 996SF 1 bedroom, 1 bath w/carport & fireplace. Located on a nice corner lot that's over 11, 000 SF. Gas forced air heat, washer/dryer for each unit w/off street parking. Interiors are in good condition & nicely laid out for comfortable living. Currently a 6 CAP w/room for upside. Don't miss out on this incredible investment opportunity!

This nearly half-acre lot has views of Burrows Bay, the San Juan Islands, and the distant twinkling lights of the Skyline Marina at night. With a towering maple and evergreen trees dotting the landscape, this mostly cleared, gently sloping lot provides the perfect canvas for your dream home. Lot certification is in progress. Concept design drawings have been completed. Utilities are in the street. Soil sample results are available for septic system design. Whether you're looking to build your forever home or a vacation retreat, imagine waking up each morning to the soothing sounds of nature and sipping your morning coffee as you take in the views!

Welcome to this water view home in Skyline! Featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and 2800+ sq ft, this property is a hidden gem. While it's a project house in need of TLC, it boasts great bones and fireplaces on both floors. The finished daylight basement offers ample space, complemented by an additional room with a hot tub and wet bar, suitable for various purposes. Enjoy the tranquility of the private backyard and the expansive deck, though it could benefit from refurbishment. Complete with a 2-car garage and low HOA, this home presents an incredible opportunity for those seeking to make it their own.

One level craftsman home in Mount Vernon's Highland Greens neighborhood. 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, open kitchen with 42 cabinets, quartz, SS appliances, pantry, and designer flooring. Primary bedroom with 5 piece attached bathroom including glass shower enclosure and soaking tub along with walk-in-closet with tons of storage and hanging. Fully fenced yard, upgraded landscaping, utility shed, and covered patio for use year round. This home was built with over $25, 000 in upgrades and has been additionally upgraded since. Centrally located close to shopping, hospital and numerous dining options. Just 8 minutes to I5 for an easy commute! Brand new carpet March 2024.

Absolutely amazing 4 bed plus office/den home in quiet cul-de-sac. Updates & upgrades are abundant throughout including AC mini splits, hickory hardwood upstairs, & much more. Lovely downstairs layout w/formal dining, office/den, & immaculate kitchen. Includes new sink & disposal, granite counters, & 2 pantries. Kitchen looks upon breakfast nook & formal living room w/gas fireplace & new fan. Upstairs primary ensuite accompanied by 2 spare bedrooms, one w/walk-in closet, & 4th bedroom/full media room. Includes projector & sound system. Valley views from this meticulously landscaped & fully fenced lot. Complete w/full upper & lower decks for phenomenal outdoor living. Close to amenities in walkable neighborhood w/Little Mountain Park trails.
